title: Top Floor 2 Bedroom Beauty East Humboldt Park
posting_body: Top Floor 2 Bedroom Beauty East Humboldt Park
Come check out this great vintage apartment with modern upgrades!
Great living area with loads of natural light.
1 bedroom includes closet, 2nd room can easily be a den or office.
Pet friendly, with some few breed restrictions.
Vibrant intersection with popular restaurants, cafes, bakeries, plant stores, shops and more!
Walking distance to the wonderful Humboldt Park and CTA bus transportation.
